addFunds(uint256).details: ERC20 approve is required to be done for this contract earlier

addToPrepaid(uint256).details: ERC20 approve needs to be done

appointeeVote(address,uint256).details: need to be appointee, set by staker themselves

params._sipId: : id of SIP in staker portfolio.
params._stakerAddress: : address of initiater of this SIP.

params._token: : is EraSwap ERC20 Smart Contract Address

params._accumulationPeriodMonths: : number of months to deposit commitment amount
params._defaultPenaltyFactor: : due to missing deposits, this is per 1000
params._gracePenaltyFactor: : due to late deposits, this is per 1000
params._gracePeriodSeconds: : grace allowance to stakers to deposit monthly
params._minimumMonthlyCommitmentAmount: : minimum SIP monthly amount in exaES

params._monthId: : deposit month id starts from 1 upto as per plan
params._sipId: : id of SIP in staker portfolio.
params._stakerAddress: : address of initiater of this SIP.

getDepositDoneStatus(address,uint256,uin.return: 0 => no deposit, 1 => grace deposit, 2 => on time deposit

getDepositStatus(address,uint256,uint256.details: it is used in deposit function require statement.

params._monthId: : deposit month id to calculate status for
params._sipId: : id of SIP in staker portfolio.
params._stakerAddress: : address of initiater of this SIP.

getDepositStatus(address,uint256,uint256.return: 0 => too late, 1 => its grace time, 2 => on time

params._isNomineeWithdrawing: : different status in case of nominee withdrawl
params._sipId: : id of SIP in staker portfolio.
params._stakerAddress: : address of initiater of this SIP.
params._withdrawlMonthId: : withdrawl month id upto which to calculate returns for

getPendingWithdrawlAmount(address,uint25.return: gives available withdrawl amount upto the withdrawl month id

monthlyDeposit(address,uint256,uint256,u.details: ERC20 approve is required to be done for this contract earlier, also  fundsDeposit should be enough otherwise contract will not accept  Also, deposit can also be done by any nominee of this SIP.

params._sipId: : id of SIP in staker address portfolio
params._stakerAddress: : address of staker who has an SIP

newSIP(uint256,uint256,bool).details: ERC20 approve is required to be done for this contract earlier, also  fundsDeposit should be enough otherwise contract will not accept

params._monthlyCommitmentAmount: : needs to be more than minimum specified in plan.

params._addresses: : address array to send prepaid ES for SIP
params._amounts: : prepaid ES for SIP amounts to send to corresponding addresses

params._newAppointeeStatus: : true or false, should this have appointee rights or not.
params._sipId: : id of SIP in staker portfolio.

params._newNomineeStatus: : true or false, whether this should be a nominee or not.
